296
00:12:48,880 --> 00:12:50,440
he'd get Si Lili out of the dungeon

297
00:12:50,640 --> 00:12:52,440
and keep her safe

298
00:12:52,440 --> 00:12:53,440
if she tells the truth.

299
00:12:56,200 --> 00:12:57,000
Let's go to the Investigator's Office.

300
00:12:57,470 --> 00:13:00,030
Your Excellency, don't panic so much.

301
00:13:00,350 --> 00:13:01,550
Maybe Miss Si Lili

302
00:13:01,710 --> 00:13:03,320
