307
00:13:07,960 --> 00:13:08,760
that is, she knows that

308
00:13:08,760 --> 00:13:10,000
the Investigator's Office thinks highly of me.

309
00:13:10,320 --> 00:13:11,110
So, she wouldn't tell the truth

310
00:13:11,110 --> 00:13:12,230
as long as she's imprisoned

311
00:13:12,470 --> 00:13:13,440
