313
00:13:16,230 --> 00:13:17,910
She'll sell me down the river.

314
00:13:18,640 --> 00:13:20,150
If Si Lili tells the truth,

315
00:13:20,670 --> 00:13:22,080
the Crown Prince, the Prime Minister

316
00:13:22,280 --> 00:13:23,200
and even His Majesty

317
00:13:23,880 --> 00:13:24,590
would think

318
00:13:24,590 --> 00:13:26,000
it's me that killed Lin Gong.

319
