329
00:14:23,840 --> 00:14:25,230
It's urgent.

330
00:14:25,590 --> 00:14:27,280
You'll die if she's alive.

331
00:14:27,670 --> 00:14:28,760
But it's of no use to kill her.

332
00:14:29,000 --> 00:14:30,080
If Si Lili is killed at this moment,

333
00:14:30,400 --> 00:14:31,590
it just proves I want to do away with a witness.

334
00:14:32,710 --> 00:14:33,710
We can say

335
00:14:33,710 --> 00:14:35,760
it's the secret agents from Beiqi that did it.

