339
00:14:39,790 --> 00:14:40,440
Why?

340
00:14:40,470 --> 00:14:41,280
Because he has never believed

341
00:14:41,280 --> 00:14:42,840
Ruoruo would support himself.

342
00:14:42,960 --> 00:14:44,000
He told her about it

343
00:14:44,350 --> 00:14:45,470
just to let her send word to me

344
00:14:45,760 --> 00:14:46,710
so that I'd respond.

345
00:14:48,710 --> 00:14:50,320
So, what can we do to solve the dilemma?

346
00:14:50,670 --> 00:14:52,080
I just hope

347
00:14:52,080 --> 00:14:53,230
someone can stop him

348
00:14:53,230 --> 00:14:54,320
