00:19:51,560 --> 00:19:52,640
What happened to his legs?

427
00:19:55,110 --> 00:19:55,880
That very year,

428
00:19:56,710 --> 00:19:58,430
Head Chen travelled hundreds of miles

429
00:19:58,760 --> 00:20:00,040
with black knights

