447
00:20:59,710 --> 00:21:00,680
Go away!

448
00:21:01,950 --> 00:21:03,950
Go away!

449
00:21:05,110 --> 00:21:06,310
He's so tough.

450
00:21:08,830 --> 00:21:09,800
What are you doing?

451
00:21:11,280 --> 00:21:13,280
Go away!

452
00:21:25,190 --> 00:21:26,190
Protect His Highness.

453
00:21:27,470 --> 00:21:28,430
Go away!

454
00:21:28,880 --> 00:21:29,640
Chen Pingping!

455
00:21:30,000 --> 00:21:30,680
Let go of me.

