00:21:30,800 --> 00:21:32,950
Chen Pingping!

457
00:21:36,230 --> 00:21:37,230
Chen Pingping!

458
00:21:38,000 --> 00:21:39,190
Protecting Crown Prince

459
00:21:39,230 --> 00:21:40,310
