00:29:00,310 --> 00:29:01,400
Nobody would listen to him?

581
00:29:03,800 --> 00:29:05,040
There is something you don't know.

582
00:29:05,760 --> 00:29:06,680
Nowadays,

583
00:29:06,920 --> 00:29:08,830
there are more and more people

584
00:29:09,040 --> 00:29:10,640
who're willing to die for Nanqing.

585
00:29:12,190 --> 00:29:13,230
They're so loyal

586
00:29:13,520 --> 00:29:14,560
that they can't tolerate

587
00:29:14,560 --> 00:29:16,230
a little mistake.

588
00:29:16,830 --> 00:29:17,950
Then they've become

589
00:29:17,950 --> 00:29:19,470
more and more ruthless.

590
00:29:20,350 --> 00:29:21,190
Even Head

591
00:29:21,190 --> 00:29:23,040
can dare not criticize such loyalty.

592
00:29:24,000 --> 00:29:27,000
I'm lazy by nature.

593
00:29:27,590 --> 00:29:28,680
I failed to change with the times.

594
00:29:28,680 --> 00:29:30,590
I failed to keep pace with them.

595
00:29:30,800 --> 00:29:31,800
So,

596
00:29:32,070 --> 00:29:34,000
I wanted to quit.

597
00:29:34,230 --> 00:29:34,920
Where are you

598
00:29:34,920 --> 00:29:35,830
going in the future?

599
00:29:36,640 --> 00:29:38,400
Where could I go?

600
00:29:38,400 --> 00:29:39,110
Of course

601
00:29:39,110 --> 00:29:40,710
I'll keep serving you.

602
00:29:43,640 --> 00:29:44,950
I see. I see.

603
00:29:45,070 --> 00:29:47,070
I did lie to you.

604
00:29:47,590 --> 00:29:49,000
I'll do something to show my apology.

605
00:29:50,000 --> 00:29:51,190
What are you going to do?

606
00:30:00,160 --> 00:30:01,070
Hold on.

607
00:30:06,920 --> 00:30:07,710
What are you doing?

608
00:30:14,430 --> 00:30:15,310
Your Excellency.

609
00:30:16,560 --> 00:30:18,520
I'll treat you on tasty food. It's on me.

610
00:30:19,000 --> 00:30:21,350
Let's go enjoy ourselves.

611
00:30:30,110 --> 00:30:30,830
Hold on.

612
00:30:31,110 --> 00:30:32,920
I don't have enough money.

613
00:30:33,640 --> 00:30:35,400
I'll pay for 1.5 bowls of noodles.

614
00:30:35,560 --> 00:30:36,590
Can you give me two bowls?

615
00:30:36,590 --> 00:30:37,590
No. No way.

616
00:30:38,040 --> 00:30:39,040
I'm not done talking. Look.

617
00:30:39,800 --> 00:30:41,000
Only one bowl

618
00:30:41,230 --> 00:30:42,230
with minced meat.

619
00:30:42,430 --> 00:30:43,160
Just add some soup

620
00:30:43,160 --> 00:30:44,430
to the other bowl.

621
00:30:44,590 --> 00:30:45,760
Is it okay?

622
00:30:46,230 --> 00:30:46,920
Okay.

623
00:30:47,430 --> 00:30:48,400
You're flexible enough.

624
00:30:48,800 --> 00:30:49,590
Okay.

625
00:30:56,520 --> 00:30:57,350
Your Excellency.

626
00:30:57,560 --> 00:30:58,800
Here you are.

627
00:31:00,800 --> 00:31:01,590
Okay.

628
00:31:01,920 --> 00:31:03,470
It looks small in size,

629
00:31:04,640 --> 00:31:06,680
but the taste is very special.

630
00:31:07,040 --> 00:31:08,640
Enjoy it. I've paid for it.

631
00:31:08,880 --> 00:31:10,110
The two bowls of noodles look different.

632
00:31:11,950 --> 00:31:12,760
You're right.

633
00:31:13,040 --> 00:31:13,680
The essence of the noodles

634
00:31:14,040 --> 00:31:15,640
lies in the soup.

635
00:31:16,470 --> 00:31:19,190
You'll know its original taste and flavor like this.

636
00:31:19,680 --> 00:31:20,950
All the extra toppings

637
00:31:21,000 --> 00:31:22,070
have been omitted.

638
00:31:22,230 --> 00:31:23,110
They're omitted.

639
00:31:23,520 --> 00:31:23,880
Come on.

640
00:31:23,880 --> 00:31:24,800
Eat while they're hot.

641
00:31:25,880 --> 00:31:29,560
These toppings are unnecessary.

642
00:31:32,310 --> 00:31:33,430
Chen Pingping

643
00:31:33,430 --> 00:31:35,470
is a monster from Heaven.

644
00:31:35,640 --> 00:31:37,110
He looks different from us.

645
00:31:37,560 --> 00:31:38,640
Humans

646
00:31:38,920 --> 00:31:40,310
have two eyes,

647
00:31:40,800 --> 00:31:41,880
but Chen Pingping

648
00:31:41,880 --> 00:31:43,310
has three more eyes

649
00:31:43,310 --> 00:31:45,280
between the two like ours.

650
00:31:45,590 --> 00:31:47,950
Most of us have two arms,

651
00:31:48,110 --> 00:31:49,950
but Chen Pingping

652
00:31:49,950 --> 00:31:51,400
has two more on his back.

653
00:31:51,520 --> 00:31:54,640
With edged tools in his hands, he's awe-inspiring.

654
00:31:56,880 --> 00:31:58,110
Five eyes?

655
00:31:59,000 --> 00:32:00,070
Four arms?

656
00:32:00,190 --> 00:32:00,880
Exactly.

657
00:32:01,830 --> 00:32:02,800
His Excellency Chen

658
00:32:03,280 --> 00:32:05,710
is over three meters high.

659
00:32:07,110 --> 00:32:11,040
His face looks like a door plank
and his fist like a hammer.

660
00:32:11,470 --> 00:32:13,000
He has a large, fierce-looking mouth.

661
00:32:14,070 --> 00:32:16,590
When he shouts at the town,

662
00:32:16,590 --> 00:32:19,430
a roll of thunder

663
00:32:19,430 --> 00:32:21,280
will crash in the sky immediately.

664
00:32:22,430 --> 00:32:24,920
Every night,

665
00:32:24,920 --> 00:32:27,310
Chen Pingping would go to the army barracks of Beiqi

666
00:32:27,310 --> 00:32:31,040
and eat over ten soldiers.

667
00:32:31,110 --> 00:32:33,280
Having got used to it,

668
00:32:33,520 --> 00:32:35,880
the Beiqi forces draw lots

669
00:32:35,880 --> 00:32:37,920
to wait to be eaten by him.

670
00:32:38,400 --> 00:32:40,040
Dear all, in a word,

671
00:32:40,040 --> 00:32:42,430
Chen Pingping is brave and battlewise

672
00:32:42,430 --> 00:32:46,230
and can even move mountains.

673
00:33:00,280 --> 00:33:01,190
How do you like it, Your Excellency?

674
00:33:02,430 --> 00:33:03,190
Not bad.

675
00:33:04,040 --> 00:33:06,710
So, you've forgiven me, right?

676
00:33:06,880 --> 00:33:07,680
I have to think about it.

677
00:33:09,280 --> 00:33:10,680
Let me get you more soup.

678
00:33:10,680 --> 00:33:11,400
Okay?

679
00:33:11,430 --> 00:33:12,160
That's enough.

680
00:33:13,590 --> 00:33:14,230
Young Master.

681
00:33:15,040 --> 00:33:16,520
Why are you still here eating?

682
00:33:16,800 --> 00:33:17,680
Why are you here?

683
00:33:18,070 --> 00:33:20,040
I just listened to stories in the tea house.

684
00:33:20,800 --> 00:33:21,920
Why did you go there?

685
00:33:22,760 --> 00:33:23,680
Our bookstore

686
00:33:23,680 --> 00:33:24,880
is going to open.

687
00:33:24,950 --> 00:33:26,680
Why are you so neglectful?

688
00:33:26,830 --> 00:33:27,800
We should spend more time

689
00:33:27,800 --> 00:33:28,560
collecting relevant information.

690
00:33:30,000 --> 00:33:31,280
I just heard a new story.

691
00:33:31,950 --> 00:33:32,830
"Chen Pingping

692
00:33:33,470 --> 00:33:35,800
Travelled Hundreds of Miles to Beiqi Alone."

693
00:33:36,350 --> 00:33:37,230
It's amazing.

694
00:33:37,590 --> 00:33:38,760
If you write a book about it,

695
00:33:38,880 --> 00:33:39,640
it'll definitely sell well.

696
00:33:40,230 --> 00:33:40,920
Chen Pingping?

697
00:33:41,430 --> 00:33:42,310
Travelled hundreds of miles?

698
00:33:42,800 --> 00:33:43,470
Alone.

699
00:33:50,520 --> 00:33:51,350
Eunuch Hou.

700
00:33:55,280 --> 00:33:56,070
Mr. Fan.

701
00:33:56,310 --> 00:33:58,040
His Majesty wants to see you. It's urgent.

702
00:33:58,680 --> 00:33:59,920
I'm not done with the noodles.

703
00:34:00,430 --> 00:34:01,560
There is no time for delay.

704
00:34:01,950 --> 00:34:03,350
They're all waiting for you.

705
00:34:06,920 --> 00:34:08,360
Eunuch Hou, how did you know I was there?

706
00:34:09,080 --> 00:34:09,950
You were not at home,

707
00:34:10,560 --> 00:34:11,670
so I went to the Investigator's Office.

708
00:34:11,910 --> 00:34:13,080
Head Chen told me you were there.

709
00:34:14,710 --> 00:34:15,710
Chen Pingping?

710
00:34:16,870 --> 00:34:17,710
The Investigator's Office

711
00:34:18,150 --> 00:34:19,470
can find anyone

712
00:34:19,470 --> 00:34:21,280
in the capital city easily.

713
00:34:21,710 --> 00:34:23,470
He found me so quickly.

714
00:34:23,560 --> 00:34:24,950
He must have sent someone to tail after me.

715
00:34:25,910 --> 00:34:26,840
Mr. Fan,

716
00:34:27,280 --> 00:34:28,560
what Head Chen wants to do

717
00:34:29,040 --> 00:34:30,870
is not something we should think about.

718
00:34:36,760 --> 00:34:37,520
Young Master,

719
00:34:37,950 --> 00:34:39,430
your brother said

720
00:34:39,430 --> 00:34:40,800
he'd treat me on noodles,

721
00:34:41,080 --> 00:34:42,000
but he left

722
00:34:42,040 --> 00:34:42,950
before he paid.

723
00:34:43,280 --> 00:34:45,470
Can you give the money to me?

724
00:34:46,150 --> 00:34:46,870
I'll pay for it.

725
00:34:48,910 --> 00:34:49,470
How much?

726
00:34:52,470 --> 00:34:53,470
Three taels of silver.

727
00:34:53,670 --> 00:34:54,560
Three taels?

728
00:34:54,600 --> 00:34:55,520
Yeah. It's cheap.

729
00:34:56,280 --> 00:34:57,320
For the two bowls of noodles?

730
00:34:59,760 --> 00:35:00,600
Even without meat.

731
00:35:01,760 --> 00:35:03,560
It's profitable.

732
00:35:03,600 --> 00:35:04,710
More profitable than opening a bookstore.

733
00:35:05,120 --> 00:35:05,670
How about like this?

734
00:35:05,710 --> 00:35:06,390
I'll buy the store

735
00:35:06,390 --> 00:35:07,390
tomorrow.

736
00:35:07,520 --> 00:35:09,150
The money you paid today will be considered your shares.

737
00:35:09,630 --> 00:35:11,600
Great! I'll make a fortune.

738
00:35:14,080 --> 00:35:15,390
He wouldn't even pay a cent.

739
00:35:25,080 --> 00:35:26,950
Mr. Fan, hold on please.

740
00:35:27,390 --> 00:35:28,560
Let me tell His Majesty about it.

741
00:35:40,560 --> 00:35:41,320
Prime Minister.

742
00:35:42,870 --> 00:35:45,230
I saw you from the distance.

743
00:35:45,670 --> 00:35:48,150
You have nothing to lose by calling me uncle.

744
00:35:48,760 --> 00:35:50,560
Uncle, you're also here.

745
00:35:51,080 --> 00:35:51,910
His Majesty said

746
00:35:52,430 --> 00:35:54,360
it's something about Gong'er's death.

747
00:35:55,470 --> 00:35:56,360
It's a serious issue.

748
00:35:56,630 --> 00:35:57,710
Shall we talk about it just in the Imperial Study?

749
00:35:59,870 --> 00:36:03,430
With His Majesty there, there will be no room for maneuver.

750
00:36:09,230 --> 00:36:11,150
Prime Minister. Mr. Fan.

751
00:36:11,150 --> 00:36:12,080
This way, please.

752
00:36:16,320 --> 00:36:18,430
Don't be afraid. Follow me.

753
00:36:49,040 --> 00:36:49,910
Your Majesty.

754
00:36:50,600 --> 00:36:52,320
Prime Minister and Mr. Fan are here.

755
00:36:54,040 --> 00:36:54,760
Let them in.

756
00:37:01,190 --> 00:37:02,190
Your Majesty.

757
00:37:06,150 --> 00:37:07,470
They're here.

758
00:37:07,560 --> 00:37:08,280
You can make things clear

759
00:37:08,710 --> 00:37:10,230
in their presence.

760
00:37:13,600 --> 00:37:16,950
Prepare a seat and some tea for Prime Minister.

761
00:37:17,760 --> 00:37:18,760
Thank you, Your Majesty.

762
00:37:24,150 --> 00:37:25,470
Your Majesty, how about me?

763
00:37:27,870 --> 00:37:28,630
You?

764
00:37:30,230 --> 00:37:31,280
Just stand here.

765
00:37:33,870 --> 00:37:36,760
Your Highness, you don't need to bow to me.

766
00:37:37,080 --> 00:37:39,000
The Investigator's Office has checked Lin Gong's body.

767
00:37:39,120 --> 00:37:41,040
He was killed by a skilled swordsman with a fast sword.

768
00:37:41,710 --> 00:37:42,840
Among all swordsmen in the capital city,

769
00:37:44,390 --> 00:37:46,360
only Xie Bi'an that works for the Second Prince

770
00:37:47,040 --> 00:37:48,190
has the ability to do that.

771
00:37:49,000 --> 00:37:50,470
Do you mean...

772
00:37:50,520 --> 00:37:51,430
He means

773
00:37:51,430 --> 00:37:52,910
I'm the one who killed Lin Gong.

774
00:37:54,560 --> 00:37:56,150
Are you the killer?

775
00:37:57,040 --> 00:37:58,230
You have to ask Fan Xian about it.

776
00:37:59,430 --> 00:38:00,190
Your Highness,

777
00:38:00,360 --> 00:38:01,470
how is it related to me?

778
00:38:02,390 --> 00:38:04,040
During 9 a.m. to 11 a.m. of the day
when Lin Gong was killed,

779
00:38:04,040 --> 00:38:05,670
I happened to meet Fan Xian on the street

780
00:38:05,670 --> 00:38:06,120
and we had a small talk.

781
00:38:06,120 --> 00:38:07,910
Xie Bi'an was also there.

782
00:38:08,280 --> 00:38:09,430
I just asked you to be here to give witness.

783
00:38:10,470 --> 00:38:11,390
Xie Bi'an is known as

784
00:38:11,430 --> 00:38:12,910
"Faster than Light."

785
00:38:13,230 --> 00:38:14,150
He is the best swordsman

786
00:38:14,320 --> 00:38:16,320
in the capital city.

787
00:38:17,120 --> 00:38:18,390
Faster than light?

788
00:38:18,630 --> 00:38:19,390
Fast sword.

789
00:38:20,760 --> 00:38:21,390
Is it true?

790
00:38:22,950 --> 00:38:24,040
Yes.

791
00:38:24,120 --> 00:38:25,950
The Investigator's Office has confirmed

792
00:38:26,760 --> 00:38:28,390
Lin Gong was killed during 9 a.m. to 11 a.m.

793
00:38:29,040 --> 00:38:30,150
In this case,

794
00:38:30,230 --> 00:38:32,150
Xie Bi'an didn't have enough time

795
00:38:32,150 --> 00:38:33,910
to rush out of town to do that.

796
00:38:34,000 --> 00:38:34,840
There is another possibility.

797
00:38:36,000 --> 00:38:37,320
Fan Xian and you joined hands

798
00:38:37,320 --> 00:38:39,390
to let Xie Bi'an kill Lin Gong.

799
00:38:39,710 --> 00:38:41,670
He was giving false testimony

800
00:38:41,910 --> 00:38:42,760
to help you stay out of it.

801
00:38:42,800 --> 00:38:43,910
It's more ridiculous.

802
00:38:44,950 --> 00:38:46,080
Why did I want to kill Lin Gong?

803
00:38:46,800 --> 00:38:48,390
Why did Fan Xian want to do that?

804
00:38:48,760 --> 00:38:51,080
Lin Gong is the one behind
the assassination attempt on Niulan Street.

805
00:38:51,360 --> 00:38:52,760
Fan Xian holds a grudge against him.

806
00:38:52,840 --> 00:38:53,670
Your Highness,

807
00:38:53,710 --> 00:38:55,000
I have no idea about that.

808
00:38:55,280 --> 00:38:56,630
He's the Crown Prince.

809
00:38:56,630 --> 00:38:58,230
We have to bear it if he wants to declare us guilty.

810
00:38:58,950 --> 00:39:00,190
Then tell me

811
00:39:00,430 --> 00:39:01,870
who else is so skilled at swordsmanship

812
00:39:02,280 --> 00:39:03,800
if it's not Xie Bi'an.

813
00:39:03,870 --> 00:39:04,950
It's not hard

814
00:39:04,950 --> 00:39:05,560
to hire a sword master

815
00:39:05,560 --> 00:39:06,670
who is unrecognized, right?

816
00:39:06,910 --> 00:39:08,320
To whom are you making pointed allusions?

817
00:39:08,320 --> 00:39:09,430
I'm just trying to reason.

818
00:39:09,670 --> 00:39:10,760
It's enough.

819
00:39:20,760 --> 00:39:21,710
Prime Minister,

820
00:39:23,360 --> 00:39:25,560
the victim is your son. What do you think?

821
00:39:28,560 --> 00:39:29,630
In my opinion,

822
00:39:32,280 --> 00:39:33,520
the person to blame

823
00:39:40,150 --> 00:39:41,630
is Chen Pingping.

824
00:39:43,040 --> 00:39:46,910
The Investigator's Office is responsible
for the safety of the capital city.

825
00:39:47,910 --> 00:39:49,910
Up to now, they haven't reported

826
00:39:50,630 --> 00:39:52,430
the truth about my son's death.

827
00:39:53,760 --> 00:39:54,710
It means Chen Pingping

828
00:39:55,430 --> 00:39:58,910
has neglected his duties.

829
00:40:01,190 --> 00:40:02,430
It makes sense.

830
00:40:05,080 --> 00:40:08,000
I hope to

831
00:40:08,320 --> 00:40:09,910
confront Chen Pingping

832
00:40:10,360 --> 00:40:12,150
and see him be punished according to law.

833
00:40:32,120 --> 00:40:33,950
It seems you enjoy standing there.

834
00:40:34,630 --> 00:40:36,430
Your Majesty, shall I kneel down?

835
00:40:39,080 --> 00:40:39,870
Rise.

836
00:40:43,000 --> 00:40:43,870
Send an imperial decree

837
00:40:44,760 --> 00:40:46,120
and ask Chen Pingping to come here.

838
00:40:47,430 --> 00:40:48,520
Got it.

839
00:41:05,600 --> 00:41:06,800
Chen Pingping!

840
00:41:08,600 --> 00:41:09,120
Your Majesty.

841
00:41:09,120 --> 00:41:10,120
Do you know your sin?

842
00:41:11,630 --> 00:41:12,560
Why do you say that?

843
00:41:13,320 --> 00:41:14,560
The Prime Minister's son was killed.

844
00:41:14,950 --> 00:41:16,520
As Head of

845
00:41:16,520 --> 00:41:17,470
the Investigator's Office,

846
00:41:17,760 --> 00:41:20,000
you haven't found out the killer up to now.

847
00:41:20,430 --> 00:41:21,560
You have to take responsibility.

848
00:41:21,840 --> 00:41:22,710
Your Majesty,

849
00:41:24,390 --> 00:41:25,950
we've found out the killer.

850
00:41:28,120 --> 00:41:29,190
You found it out?

851
00:41:30,520 --> 00:41:31,320
Good.

852
00:41:31,800 --> 00:41:35,080
In the presence of Prime Minister and others,

853
00:41:35,600 --> 00:41:37,280
tell me who is the killer.

854
00:41:45,470 --> 00:41:46,280
Prime Minister,

855
00:41:48,040 --> 00:41:50,560
I'm surprised to hear the sad news upon my return.

856
00:41:51,390 --> 00:41:54,080
I'm sorry for your loss.

857
00:41:55,280 --> 00:41:56,600
Who is the killer?

858
00:41:59,760 --> 00:42:02,800
Si Gujian from Dongyi Town.

859
00:42:03,870 --> 00:42:05,040
One of the Great Masters?

860
00:42:05,120 --> 00:42:06,120
If it were not a Great Master,

861
00:42:06,150 --> 00:42:07,840
who else could use a sword so quickly?

862
00:42:09,800 --> 00:42:11,080
As a Great Master,

863
00:42:11,150 --> 00:42:13,040
he travelled hundreds of miles to the capital city

864
